Note on phot.dat: The FTN transit (2m Faulkes Telescope North) was obtained
     through a Pan-STARRS-z filter on 2010 Feb 26. The Euler transit (1.2m)
     was obtained through a  Gunn-r filter on 2010 Apr 15.
